==Pro Tools: assign MIDI message to plug in or instrument parameter==


To assign a MIDI message to a plug in or instrument in Pro Tools hold down '''control''' and click the parameter you wish to affect. Choose learn in the pop-up menu and then move the slider or knob on your MIDI controller that is sending the MIDI message you wish to assign.

